content.detailedDescription:
Ufo was observed only when it was close enough on descent to reflect the tree line on objects dish/pan shaped bottom that arced up at edges. object was at least a mile wide and by the reflective bottom but otherwise invisible. was almost to treetop height in appearance, maybe a couple hundred feet to a hundred feet above trees,(guessing), when all just went away, or stopped reflecting. nothing else was seen.

observer described a very weird feeling and was uneasy the rest of the night.

observer called me to describe the even the next day and asked if i had any weird stuff happen the night before.

the only odd occurrence was as i was taking my medications the next morning i suddenly noticed my nose was bleeding all over my chest and running down my stomach, through my moustache and beard. a fairly heavy bleed. then a few minutes later my daughter came down from her room and had a tissue in her nose and informed me she woke up with a nose bleed too. same nostril too.

first time in over a year we had any nose bleeds around here! 

person who saw this thing has had several odd occurrences on his security cams outside his house this fall and winter. one had a light coming from above the house somewhere very brightly lighting his parking area and front porch. one had some weird light appendages moving around the porch area almost inquisitively. he swears he saw the face of a alien outside his window once that resembled the insect type with the big black eyes taking up half it's head, last fall but swears he will not admit that to anyone but me, his father.

we have made reports before of smaller objects and such, we continue to watch the sky when we can and have seen a lot of small sightings like lights that resemble satellites but turn and move in different directions. we have seen ,(until now), nothing like the big ship that came up in the north horizon and then flew overhead and straight south into space not following the horizon down again two years or so ago.
content.summary: Cloaked, about a mile wide, bottom dished, reflected trees along river upside down on bottom of dish, reflection cureved with bottom

content.detailedDescription:
Guten tag

ich möchte ein ereignis melden, das mir 1996 in einer sommernacht passiert war. ich weiß das es schon länger her ist aber damals war ich noch nicht mit den internet bzw. ich wusste da auch noch nichts von mufon. was ich jetzt hier schreibe hat sich genauso zugetan und bitte glauben sie mir. ich war damals mit mein auto zu besuch bei einem freund und kam erst spät abends um ca. 02:50 uhr nach hause. ich fuhr das auto auf unser grundstück und stieg dann aus. dann schloß ich die auto tür zu und dann sah ich es. zwei orang rot leuchtende kugeln schwebten über ein nahbarhaus. es war schwer einzuschätzen wie weit weg die objekte waren. eine kugel schien mir näher als die andere, weil sie größer war. die andete kugel war kleiner und etwas höher. die kugeln selber schien von einer feurigen aura umgeben zu sein. ähnlich wie eine übergroße orange, die mit feuer überzogen ist. vom einschätzen der kugeln, erschienen sie mir ziemlich groß. geräusche waren überhaupt keine zu hören. zu dieser zeit, gab es eine discothek (kraftwerk),in unserer nähe. draussen hatten sie ein licht strahler der muster in den himmel projizierte. ich vermute, wahrscheinlich wurde es davon angezogen. dies ganze ereignis ging ungefähr 2-3 minuten. dann waren die kugeln weg. einfach weg. kein wegfliegen oder sonst was. ich schreibe dies hier in der hoffnung, das wenigstens sie mir glauben. damals hatte ich angst dort hinzugehen, weil ich nicht wusste was passieren würde. heute bedauere ich es irgendwie ein bisschen. ich würde mich freuen wenn sie mir eine antwort schicken könnten.

mit freundlichen grüßen
content.summary: Zwei kugelförmige objekte

content.detailedDescription:
Was walking along the beach with my husband at about 1135 am on a friday. this is a quiet section of the beach as it is just residential. there is a fenced off area right on the beach that looks like it may once have been an underground military base (there are public bathrooms that go underground right near it) but the above-ground area is now used as a nature preserve for nesting birds. 

we noticed a red helicopter appear and fly above the nature preserve near where we were walking, circled 2-3 times and then left. within seconds, a black unmarked helicopter appeared and did the same thing but stayed a little longer just circling around. we were looking around to see why they might be there but couldn't see anything. it was weird. a couple of minutes later another helicopter appeared but this was a marked police copter. at that point i thought there might be something up there that was cloaked, so i started shooting video of the helicopter.  i did not see anything with the naked eye.  when i looked at the video later, i noticed a whitish-green orb with a purple ring (like saturn) around it that shot up towards the helicopter and then descended. just before the video ends, there is a very subtle showering of light. i was very surprised to see the orb and the showering of light, but believe it might be something in light of the unusual helicopter activity.
content.summary: 3 helicopters appeared for no reason, first, red, then black (unmarked), & last the police copter in video, did not see anything with naked eye only on video

content.detailedDescription:
These events happened when i was 14 years old, and it included myself and my cousin.  the day wasn't anything out of the ordinary.  during the summertime minnesota can get pretty hot, and we were in the middle of a hot summer that year.  all through the day of wandering through the local parks, swimming in the local lake, and then hanging out at my cousin's house at night we didn't experience anything out of the ordinary.  at that age we would always attempt to stay awake as long as we could and squeeze what time we could get out of the summer.

when we finally decided that we were going to go to bed, we both found ourselves uncomfortably hot.  wandering down stairs, we looked around the kitchen trying to get something to make us cold again.  fans, cold water douses, or soaked towels.  we couldn't get cool.  we weren't to the point of sickness about it, we just couldn't take the sticky heat.  and so we decided to fill a couple spray bottles normally used for fending off cats from plants, and use them to mist our faces.

we both ended up in the living room connected to the kitchen.  all the lights were off and we both were laying on the floor.  talking, laughing, complaining about how hot it was.  the living room had a wall of three windows all facing a slight rise in the ground that led upwards towards the next property.  this "divider" also had many trees planted giving it the look like a wooded area.  of course the length from just outside the window to the lawn of the next person up the hill was probably around 50-60ft.  the windows were probably around 3-4ft off the ground from their base.  and the window that was important, was the middle window.

my cousin and i talked for quite a while, trying to pass the time until exhaustion would overtake our annoyance about the heat.  very suddenly my cousin stopped talking and in the midst of misting my face, i called for him by name.  when i didn't receive a response, i looked over at him.  previously he had been laying flat on his back on the floor, spraying his face every now and again.  now when i looked over at him, he was slightly propped up on his arms and staring intently at the middle window.  a few more times i called his name, each time becoming a little bit more worried about what was going on.  of course then i decided to see what he was looking at.  when i looked over towards the middle window, i saw what he was looking at.  no limbs, no body, just the head of a creature just poking above the bottom of the window.  shape of it's head was like an upside down tear-drop, the same head that has been reported by so many people.  two very slightly slanted black eyes, and not very many other discernible facial features.  there was a direct connection, from the creature's posture i could tell that this thing and my cousin were locked onto each other.  i watched in horror for around 20 seconds before this thing turned to looked at me.  i would say we only locked gazes for about five seconds before this thing disappeared.  but it didn't just "vanish", i could see it had moved to it's left and to my right at an unbelievable speed.

i can remember so vividly that day.  i can remember getting a pizza from a certain local gas station and enjoying it with my cousin, uncle, and aunt.  i remember how it progressed into that night, playing video games until we tried to sleep.  i remember how hot it was, how heavy the air felt.  i can remember laughing about our predicament together while laying in that living room.  i don't know if i missed time, or if it was the heat, but i dont remember what happened after seeing that thing.  the next day, we were sleeping up in his room on the top floor of the house.  we both remembered seeing that thing, still to this day we could tell the story identically.  but neither of us remember how we got back to bed that day.  it was the first and only time i have seen one of these things, but it is not the first time that i have suspected something.
content.summary: An event that put the fear of grays into me

content.detailedDescription: I was driving to work at 4.30am on the 8/4/16 when something caught my peripheral vision in the early morning night sky, then all of a sudden i noticed a very bright star slowing to a halt, this happened less then a minute from work. i parked my car and looked up at the star like object, the object starting moving so i reached for my phone and took a short video of it and just before it went out of sight i took a still photo of it because on the still photo i can enlarge it. to much of my surprise it wasn't a star anymore ,it had a defined shape. because my focus was on the moving stare like object i neglected to notice at that moment that there was a larger object to the right as if it was a mother ship just standing stationary. i have since sent copies of the video and still photo to channel9 perth. i tried to upload the video and still to my home computer however it does not show the true quality of the images like my galaxy s5 phone does. my only regret is i wished i kept taking more photos because after the moving object went out of sight over a rooftop i noticed 3 white objects moving super fast straight up through the clouds then out of sight. i got the feeling the moving object i first noticed split up into three
content.summary: One large beemerang with upsidedown dome in centre. second craft rectangle with 3 black round black plated underneath

content.detailedDescription: Was taking my dogs out like i have done 100's of times. thought i heard perhaps a plane approaching. i glanced up and noticed a sort of flattened dull grey sphere at some distance, could of been a mile, hovering. initially i thought it was the plane coming directly at me, but noticed that it had stopped. as i took perhaps 10 steps closer, it casually drifted off to the left and behind some trees and carport and i lost sight. i know what a plane is. i dont think it was. im completely uncertain of what it actually was.
content.summary: Thought it was a plane coming. then no sound, hovered, trailed off to the left

content.detailedDescription:
my wife and i were about to run to 7/11 when we noticed several objects that were all shaped exactly the same. the 4 objects were not in a group but spaced out across the sky of west bradenton florida.  we originally thought the objects were stars but the objects began to move across the sky-- we then figured they had to be planes even though they looked nothing like any planes we ever saw-- we just chalked it up to the sky playing tricks on our eyes. 
 the objects that look like 4 separate strings of pulsating beads moved in slightly different direction but all 4 headed toward the same westerly general area , what appeared to be a planned direction or location . 2 of the objects changed directions as we watched.  
 they objects also seemed to gain altitude as they were moving , after about an hour 15 mins the objects stopped dead in the sky in 4 different locations. as i type this report they are currently hanging in the sky on the extreme west of bradenton .  the pulsating of the lights seems to have increased especially in 2 of the objects. the lights appear to be white, red and blue/green but are pulsating in unison not separately.   
 the scary and worrisome part of this whole thing is it feels to me as if they traveled and then stopped in what i only can describe as a pattern that makes me feel unsafe. like they are stationed there to observe something or be ready to initiate some type maneuver. i just walked back outside and all objects are still there clear as day but 2 have moved very slightly from there original parked position of about an hour ago . 
 to be honest my wife is freaked out --- what comes to my mind is a few days ago nasa launched a rocket that basically flys right over bradenton , it just seems like this situation is related in some way to the rocket launch . --it's 23:30 currently and no change...Still there
content.summary: My wife and i saw and are still looking at 4 separate objects that look like a line of pulsating beads. we wat ched them travel across the sky from ne to west ..They ae currently hovering in the sky west of bradenton toward the beach .

content.detailedDescription: I was getting the mail l when i noticed a shape in the sky. it wasn't super close, but it was distinguishable. i didn't see any sort of resemblence to a plane as it didn't leave any trail, it had no wings, and it had no lights. it slowly moved towards the north as i observed it for a while before running inside to get my camera. at this time i had no good camera and my pictures showed barely more than a blurry spec, i since lost that camera and have not gotten pictures since. it notably appears every summer from what i have observed, any time from july to august. it has been the same shape consistantly. it always is in about the same spot, but it has moved in other directions. i never stay out too long as aliens both fascinate and scare me.
content.summary: Every summer for the past 3 years i have the same ufo that hovers for a bit and continues on its way

content.detailedDescription:
I went outside at 10:45pm to look for ufos. i heard a helicopter in the distance 5 mins later and saw a military helicopter hovering and circling. 

the helicopter would circle, hover and then come over near my house and the move away again. i wondered what it was looking for. 

after a few mins of these antics, i saw a bright light , and orb throwing off amazing colours, moving towards the helicopter! 

the ufo went right up to the helicopter , only a few feet away! and moved upwards at a fast speed above it into the sky. 

the first thought i had was "it was taunting the military chopper haha" 

i laughed, amazed and in awe at this spectacle


the helicopter left after 10 mins. the ufo stayed right where it was, up in the sky, pretending to be a star. i got the impression that the military helicopter was satisfied it was staying where it was where no one could witness it and left. 

the ufo stayed there for over an hour! i was surprised no one else saw this all! 

i looked online at the worthing town page on facebook and everyone spotted the helicopter or heard it but not the ufo. i am puzzled. 

i also saw on your ufo stalker page that someone in paignton devon, 3 hours away from where i live saw the same thing on the 7th april, just a day before!!
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Military helicopter chasing ufo - ufo taunting the helicopter

content.detailedDescription:
Kingswood bristol uk

22:00

looking at stars.

blue flashing light drew my attention to this object.

it was the size of a star, it pulsed brightly, blue, green, red, orange, white, yellow.

blue was the brightest most striking colour.

it did not appear to move.

we watched for over an hour before it disappeared over the south horizon.

a plane flew over head whilst watching the object.

none of the other stars disappeared over the horizon like this did.

i called my parents in hanham bristol uk and they could see the same object and described it the same as i have. 

my mum informed me that she could see a second light pulsing object further in the distance, this was not visible from my house.

our camera would not photograph this object.

i was mesmerised by the pulsating changing of colours, i could not take my eyes off it.
content.summary: Bright pulsing light, multicoloured, no particular sequence, did not appear to move. watched for over an hour, disappeared from over south horizon.

content.detailedDescription:
I've noticed these lights for about a year now. they are always in the same position in the sky (from my bedroom). i have not only seen them from my bedroom but in a number of places. 
the lights always occur when there is heavy cloud. the first time i witnessed this, there were 3 lights. at first i thought it was searchlights looking towards the sky. but searchlights don't move this quickly. you can see the lights move towards the left, stop, then move to the right and stop again. it's always the same place in the sky where it stops and then goes back. the first time i have seen them i must have been watching them for about 10-20 minutes. i had to stop looking because it was getting late. i have tried to take pictures of this but they don't appear clearly or at all on the photo.
i have seen these lights in manchester town centre and in reddish as well. 
i want to find out if these lights are indeed searchlights looking up at the sky or something else. i am looking forward to hearing back from you and if anyone else in the manchester area has come forward and registered anything similar.
content.summary: Lights in sky above clouds

content.detailedDescription: I live in queens, ny. on april 8, 2016 at about 10:30 pm, i was closing the bedroom window getting ready for bed, looked out the window and noticed a bright pulsating light in the sky. at first i thought it was a star then i realized this was first blinking (non-airplane type blinking) and pulsating more and more. i grabbed by video camera to record and each time i zoomed in, object seemed to be omitting different types of lights, almost looked like beams coming from it. at one point, looked like shooting beams coming from it then after a while, started to drift behind clouds. i lost it for a minute then regained observation. recorded about 20 minutes of this object then lost it behind clouds again. i never regained visual of the object. it definitely was not a plane, not the moon, not a drone or helicopter. i showed it to my girlfriend who doesn't believe in any of these things and she was freaked out by this video.
content.summary: Pulsating light in the sky, stationary at first then slowly drifting towards the east. lost behind clouds.

content.detailedDescription: While driving in neighborhood as i past elementary school athletic field noticed bright light in sky. light did not move. parked car. got out. stood in field to look. sky dark. no stars. clear view of sky and object. no surrounding buildings other lights or obstructions. saw dark triangular object. black on black sky with bright white light in center. light did not cast beam. hard to determine size, height of object in sky. narrow point of triangle faced me. hovered entire time. no sound. noticed small red and green flashing lights similar to an aircraft slowly blinking on and off at either side of the largest two points of triangle. from my vantage point estimate the size of object to be about twice size of an automobile. object remained still. i stood and watched it for about 5 minutes. when i left the object was still there. first sighting. not sure if it is ufo or drone. live in d.C. metro area. maybe 20 miles from dulles int'l airport so see various size airplanes often. never saw anything like this.
content.summary: Black,triangular. bright white light in center. not blinding. small red and green blinking lights at largest area of triangle.
